OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773389069
OL,3,CPat Sharp unveils 1996 UK high street
OL,4,Cmodel at Legoland Windsor
OL,6,FPat Sharp has reflected on his time as
OL,7,Fa TV presenter for popular gameshow
OL,8,FFun House as a "nice memory" as he
OL,9,Fremembered the 1990s.
OL,11,FThe broadcaster reminisced on the
OL,12,Fdecade as he unveiled a new attraction
OL,13,Finspired by the era at Legoland
OL,14,FWindsor, to commemorate the 30th
OL,15,Fanniversary of the theme park.
OL,17,FSharp, 64, was the face of the hit ITV
OL,18,Fchildren's show for a decade. In the
OL,19,Fshow contestants competed for prizes
OL,20,Fincluding toys, games and holidays.
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@\O]
