PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773389069
OL,3,CPat Sharp unveils 1996 UK high street
OL,4,Cmodel at Legoland Windsor
OL,6,FSpeaking about the era, he said: "The
OL,7,F'90s were very colourful for me,
OL,8,Fbecause I was doing Fun House
OL,9,Fthroughout the whole decade, and this
OL,10,Fwas the biggest kid show pretty much
OL,11,Fof all time, I think.
OL,13,F"It was on a Friday afternoon, and my
OL,14,Fclothes were leery and bright, and the
OL,15,Fgames were messy and gungy, and there
OL,16,Fwere Go Karts, and there was fun-
OL,17,Ffilled games, and it was just bright
OL,18,Fand colourful, much like Legoland.
OL,19,FIt's a nice memory for me.
OL,26,@nD@bOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
