OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773389069
OL,3,CPat Sharp unveils 1996 UK high street
OL,4,Cmodel at Legoland Windsor
OL,6,F"I've done lots of shows, but that's
OL,7,Fmy best known one, and the one I'm
OL,8,Fmost sort of known for.
OL,10,F"I get so many people saying to me,
OL,11,Flike, 'Oh, you made my childhood
OL,12,Fbecause there were only four (TV)
OL,13,Fchannels and I didn't have Facebook'.
OL,14,FSo it's a really nice accolade for me."
OL,16,FSharp has teamed up with Legoland
OL,17,FWindsor to unveil its latest addition
OL,18,Fto its Miniland attraction, which
OL,19,Fshowcases miniature recreations of
OL,20,Fworld landmarks.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@gO]
