PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773389069
OL,3,CPat Sharp unveils 1996 UK high street
OL,4,Cmodel at Legoland Windsor
OL,6,FThe new addition to the theme park,
OL,7,Ftitled 1996 High Street, has been
OL,8,Fdescribed as a nostalgic tribute to
OL,9,FBritish '90s culture, and includes
OL,10,Fminiature figures of pop bands, shop
OL,11,Fsignage and football scenes from the
OL,12,Fera.
OL,14,FThe model, which took more than 171
OL,15,Fhours to create, will be on display in
OL,16,FMiniland until the end of the year.
OL,18,FSharp said: "I'm absolutely chuffed to
OL,19,Fbe part of Legoland Windsor Resort's
OL,20,F30th birthday celebrations.
OL,26,@zD@MOU
