PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773389069
OL,3,CPat Sharp unveils 1996 UK high street
OL,4,Cmodel at Legoland Windsor
OL,6,F"Stepping in as the honorary model
OL,7,Fmaker to add the finishing touches to
OL,8,F'1996 High Street' is pure '90s magic.
OL,10,F"This scene is bursting with nostalgia
OL,11,Fand brilliant details, and I can't
OL,12,Fwait for families to see it and relive
OL,13,Fthat 'wow' moment from the year the
OL,14,Fattraction first opened."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@YO]
