PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773389069
OL,3,CPat Sharp unveils 1996 UK high street
OL,4,Cmodel at Legoland Windsor
OL,6,FVice president at Legoland Windsor
OL,7,FResort, Ramesh Ganeson, said: "As we
OL,8,Fcelebrate our 30th year, it's
OL,9,Ffantastic to see generations of
OL,10,Ffamilies come together to create even
OL,11,Fmore awesome memories where
OL,12,Fimaginations and creativity unleash in
OL,13,Fthe world of play.
OL,15,F"It's the perfect opportunity to
OL,16,Freflect on the iconic '90s era and
OL,17,Fencourage families of all ages to
OL,18,Fbuild with us year after year.
OL,26,@oD@_OUwD@AOU
