OL,3,CPat Sharp unveils 1996 UK high street
OL,4,Cmodel at Legoland Windsor
OL,6,F"Unveiling our new '1996 High Street'
OL,7,Fscene in Miniland is the perfect way
OL,8,Fto rewind and reflect on where all the
OL,9,Ffun began in March 1996."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
